{"tid":1847762,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"今次洩漏病毒, 下次就係輻射","createTime":"2020-01-28T07:48:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T07:53:20.000Z","uid":206117,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d918a702594de63691ebfe18521efb3981edc921","tid":1847762,"uid":206117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:48:36.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n哩片大陸真係計時炸彈黎<br />\n就算香港立國佢都一樣可以有意無意同你攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"103690674ac64c4be6805922786376cd81e92d03","tid":1847762,"uid":49336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:49:04.000Z","msg":"大亞灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b719f3f122ca4daa95dd0f5edc2f5a008f696f79","tid":1847762,"uid":321977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:49:48.000Z","msg":"輻射漏左都無人知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5977532f8c6f42fe0ba370bb86551dd67b568924","tid":1847762,"uid":54930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:49:56.000Z","msg":"睇到個標題嚇到叫左出黎，老細問咩事，我照讀比佢聽，讀左標題內文都未開始讀，佢成塊面白哂，自言自語，猛咁話「共慘輻射殺到黎，香港九龍新界無得避，要化身玉皇大帝打救蒼生；共慘輻射殺到黎，香港九龍新界無得避，要化身玉皇大帝打救蒼生&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n跟住衝左上天台，叫左一聲「鳴呀，點解係我」就跳左落去，成班同事追上去都追唔切，有兩個女同事嚇到暈左，仲有個男同事當場嚇到變左弱智，不停問人要唔要食腸仔蛋。<br />\n<br />\n我就好好彩無咩事，但同班同事五十幾個人即時變左失業，你條仆街真係害人害物&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"db9b128b156956430f7e4f9ea04d9ece2a10d9d9","tid":1847762,"uid":124983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:51:52.000Z","msg":"預演<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"714eed43520e05e3ab573750146487567e43e0c5","tid":1847762,"uid":317233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:52:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>熱烈欢迎全国同胞來港免费就医！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1847735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1847735</a></strong></span>"},{"pid":"014b53b5e75cab39837f4525d989ce493c0bd921","tid":1847762,"uid":206117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b719f3f122ca4daa95dd0f5edc2f5a008f696f79","tid":1847762,"uid":321977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:49:48.000Z","msg":"輻射漏左都無人知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:52:44.000Z","msg":"可以check到數字有異常<br />\n但佢唔會認係佢漏m"},{"pid":"97fa1c259ab5e5c4f2e43155479f5507b5414c32","tid":1847762,"uid":76776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:52:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ae3bedbb189b845e56de0e0515bbbe30be2960b0","tid":1847762,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:53:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔好意思阻大家少少時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但事關重大，請廣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />懇求大家盡快無限期三罷</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人以及醫護、海關等要職唔一齊三罷嘅後果，只會鼓勵更多支那感染者衝嚟香港求醫，間接促成社區爆發，害死包括醫護同海關全家在內嘅更多人<br />\n<br />\n我會支持三罷，亦會身體力行一齊三罷保護香港，直至港府落實封關<br />\n<br />\n大家唔通想犧牲香港200萬手足同自己全家條命去救呢d準備落地獄嘅人渣？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「感染的人越多越好」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aMf1RYs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaMf1RYs.jpg&h=d189414d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">把我臉上的口罩撕下來朝我吐了口吐沫，說「我活不了，你們都別想活」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XkLMVDM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXkLMVDM.jpg&h=058fd92f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">撕扯她們的防護服<br />\n「要死一起死」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i7qtpw7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi7qtpw7.jpg&h=11a8b2cc&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}